Private updateWidgetPropertiesBeforeChangingLayout

  • updateWidgetPropertiesBeforeChangingLayout(fromLayoutInfo: LayoutInfo, toLayoutId: string): this
    • Defined in jimu-for-builder/lib/app-config-actions.ts:1265

    When widget is moved between layout, widget MAY be moved into/out from another widget (like list). When the widget is moved into another widget (like list), it needs to inherit the data source info from the containing widget. When it's moved out, we need to remove the inherited data source.
